{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5210afb8aa","title":"中央国家机关和各民主党派中央机关 又一批确有改悔的右派分子摘掉帽子","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e3fb45bb6c","index":0,"year":1960,"month":11,"day":24,"articleId":"5210afb8aa"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"06bbf56893","name":"新华社"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e060c0b33e","type":"title","text":"中央国家机关和各民主党派中央机关 又一批确有改悔的右派分子摘掉帽子","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5210afb8aa"},{"id":"23949431fa","type":"authors","text":"新华社","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5210afb8aa"},{"id":"c148a51a0a","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社２４日讯中央国家机关和各民主党派中央机关根据１９５９年９月１６日中共中央、国务院关于确实表现改好了的右派分子的处理问题的决定，最近又摘掉一批确有改悔的右派分子的帽子。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5210afb8aa"},{"id":"64d136bc28","type":"paragraph","text":"这一批被宣布摘掉右派帽子的有：黄绍竑、刘王立明、钱伟长、王葆真、董渭川、宋云彬、李俊龙、李伯球、谭惕吾、邓季惺、楼邦彦、叶笃义、徐诵明、崔敬伯、王寄一、周颖、金宝善、骆介子、万枚子等二百六十多人。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5210afb8aa"},{"id":"40778ec2ee","type":"paragraph","text":" ---- 原载《人民日报》1960年11月25日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5210afb8aa"}],"page":{"id":"2ceae70227","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5210afb8aa","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}